Sri Lanka Defers Monetary Policy Announcement to May 16

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-05-12T11:13:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/sri-lanka-defers-monetary-policy-announcement-to-may-16.html
Sri Lanka  deferred its monthly
monetary policy announcement to May 16 from May 13, the central
bank said in an e-mailed statement, without giving a reason.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
